</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Replacing the general Adventurer of FF quests by different classes: <a href=".forum.t-o-m-e.net/viewtopic.php?t=2677">http://forum.t-o-m-e.net/viewtopic.php?t=2677</a> 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
